<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>KHUARUAHHAR VEL</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 A rawk cang mi, Ka thinlung ruahnak
 Zungzal thi ding, Mi a rak si,
 Nunnak ngeilo, Zungzal thi dingmi
 Na ka luatter, Na ka luatter.

[P1]
   Khuaruahhar vel, A va thlum hringhran
   Misual kei ka caah, aw aw aw
   Ka rak tlau nak, In na ka hmu cang
   Mitcaw khua ka hmu cang,

[C1]
   Aw, khua ka hmuh kho cang, a a a
   Aw, khua ka hmu kho cang, Maw Bawipa
   Na nunnak na pek, a a a
   Na nunnak na pek, Kei caah, a a.

[V2]
 A ka sertu, Nangmah na si i
 A ka khamhtu, Nangmah na si,
 Na dawtnak in, Vawlei mi vialte
 Na kan khamh cang, Na kan khamh cang.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
</song>